19/12/2003
SKOPJE, Macedonia -- Interior Minister Hari Kostov and French Ambassador to Macedonia Veronique Bujan Bore signed an agreement Thursday (18 December) to provide each other with technical and operational assistance in the fight against organised crime and terrorism. 
After the ceremony, Kostov said that Macedonia would also use France's experience and example in transforming its special task unit. 
(Dnevnik, Utrinski Vesnik - 19/12/03; MIA - 18/12/03)
